title: Before Sunrise (1995) (Opt. NL subs)
description:
IMDB: http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0112471/

Before Sunrise is a passionate and intelligent romance between a young American
(Jesse) and a French student (Celine). A chance encounter on the train incites
intrigue, and Jesse provocatively suggests that Celine postpones her return to
France and embarks instead on a spontaneous expedition to Vienna. In the course
of their 14-hour relationship, the two share in their love for the unrehearsed
and their appreciation for the unexpected as they explore in a powerful meeting
of hearts and minds.
